  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model is intended to predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device operating at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors have been evaluated; seven factors were fully assessed and six were scoped as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. The assessment team accepted the model for the stated use scope described in the Claim and Requirement nodes. Note: structured Context of Use metadata is captured in the prose of the bound Claim and Requirement rather than as a separate hasContextOfUse object.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-claim",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis",
